name: Hi, I'm Tired!
description:
Aren't we all? But NFTs and ARTS are really saving me. I've been using art as my therapy since I'm not taking any meds for my PDD(dysthymia)

Approaching 1 year in Nov since I was diagnosed with it. Still, ALIVE AND DRAWINGGG!!! 

---------------------

Collecting this and other 1/1s creation means supporting a dream of the artist to continue his craft while making a living.
Join Jakestudyos on his journey and evolution.


Thank you, I've made this with the iPad I got thru NFTS, rightful collectors, co-artists, and of course, HIC ET NUNC!

Love you all,
-Jakestudyos
